text: Edmond De Knibber was an archer from Belgium. De Knibber competed at the 1920 Summer Olympics and won three medals.Edmond DE KNIBBER He was born on 23 January 1875.Victor De Knibber == References == Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:Belgian archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for Belgium Category:Olympic silver medalists for Belgium
